== 個人生活 ==
约翰·艾略特·加德纳是牧師{{tsl|en|Rolf Gardiner|洛夫·加德纳}}之子<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.musicianguide.com/biographies/1608002389/John-Eliot-Gardiner.html |title=John Eliot Gardiner Biography |publisher=Musicianguide.com |date= |accessdate=31 October 2012 |archive-date=2021-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411091647/https://www.musicianguide.com/biographies/1608002389/John-Eliot-Gardiner.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他的祖父則是[[埃及学|埃及学]]學者{{tsl|en|Alan Gardiner|艾倫·韓德森·加德纳}}。

加德纳個人有兩段婚姻，育有三女。

